text: Cotycicuiara multifasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2008.BioLib.cz - Cotycicuiara multifasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2008
